    "en": {
      "title": "\"Ranil Rajapaksa\" is more dangerous than Rajapaksa",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Member of Parliament Hirunika Premachandra appeared before the Criminal Investigation Department at 11.00 am today and gave a statement.",
        "He accused President Ranil Wickremesinghe of trying to arrest and interrogate those involved in the protest against the government.",
        "He also said that Ranil Wickremesinghe became the President of the country after reaping the benefits of the people's struggles.",
        "Hirunika added that \"Ranil Rajapaksa\" is more of a dictator than Rajapaksa. (R)"
      ],
